hopobject.body: How many more years do you have to go? converting pristiq to venlafaxine Meanwhile, the 10.1-inch Iconia A3 tablet is a step up from the A1 announced earlier this year, running Android Jelly Bean on a quad-core 1.2GHz Cortex A7 processor and a 1,280 x 800 display. The 16GB Wi-Fi only version will cost €249 and arrive in Europe in early October, while the 3G version will cost €299. A 32GB variant is also available and both support microSD cards to expand storage.
